document_data.History:
When forces led by [[Deudermont]] and Lord [[Brambleberry]] attacked Luskan to drive out [[Arklem Greeth]] and the [[Arcane Brotherhood]] in the {{YearlinkName|1376}}, fierce resistance was expected and encountered on the Harbor Cross bridge. In particular, Lord Brambleberry's forces got pinned down by [[evocation]] [[magic]] before a large chunk of the Long Span collapsed and fell into the water. Although they won the fight, losses were high and fires on the north end resulted in innocent lives lost.

